Customer Reviews


Great selection of stories, poor execution
Â Â Â Â Â 

by
        
          ChelsMM
        
        
      

    We love the choices of stories, but there is one major flaw. The app does not save your spot in the book if the app is closed. There is an option to place a bookmark, but if the device is accidentally shut off or if the battery dies, (or if you forget to remove the last book mark and place a new one) your spot in the story is lost. Plus, every time you open the app, you have to find your story and then find your place. It doesn't even have a "currently playing" section. My kids and I find this really frustrating. This seems like it could be easily fixed. Other audiobook apps have this feature.
  




