tales2go inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Application Software
Tales2Go Inc. provides audio books for early childhood programs and primary schools. The Company offers a subscription service that streams audio book titles from leading publishers to desktops, laptops, and mobile devices. Tales2Go markets its services throughout the United States.




